Thread
------

* Thread is a light weight process or part of a process.

* excuting multiple sub processes simutanously is called multi threading
  (different flow of excutions at a time)

* This is important because in some situation we need to work with 2 or more method simutanously

* By Inter-Thread communication we achieve that.

* Perfomance of application is increased due to Multi-threading

* Multi-threading used in animations,video games etc.where we need to perform more tasks at the same time